      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "REMOTION GET DOWN - Default Pipeline\n\nThis workflow bridges ComfyUI with Remotion for programmatic video compositing.\nA starter Remotion project is bundled at TrentNodes/remotion_project/ -- no setup needed.\n\n1. PROJECT CONFIG: Defaults to the bundled project. Just leave project_path as-is.\n2. LOAD SOURCE: Load an image or connect a video batch from upstream AI generation (Wan, LTX, etc.)\n3. EXPORT FRAMES: Writes frames as PNGs into public/. frame_dir and frame_count auto-wire to Build Props.\n4. BUILD PROPS: frame_dir and frame_count come from the wire. Add title/subtitle via key-value pairs.\n5. RENDER: Calls npx remotion render -- composition_id must match one in Root.tsx (AIFrameOverlay, TitleCard)\n6. LOAD RESULT: Imports the rendered video back into ComfyUI as an IMAGE tensor batch\n\nPrereqs: Node.js 16+ (nvm install 20), ffmpeg on PATH. First run will auto npm-install deps."
      ],
      "color": "#8B6B4C",
      "bgcolor": "#3D2817"
    }
